Cell["\<\
The fully-contracted terms processed henceforth correspond to \
fully-contracted left-dressed disjoint direct contributions generated by the \
application of Wick\[CloseCurlyQuote]s theorem to the following matrix \
element (cf. expansion formula of Gorkov\[CloseCurlyQuote]s polarization \
propagator), \
